subject: Swimming
lead_paragraph: The two-time Olympic 1,500-meter gold medalist Grant Hackett qualified for a relay berth at this year’s world swimming championships in Kazan, Russia, after finishing fourth in the 200-meter freestyle at the Australian titles in Sydney, six years after he retired from the sport.
